('Blocks 3D', 4650, 'Remove all the blocks from the field in a limited amount of time. The blocks can only fly away in the direction of the arrow. Rotate the cubes to find the right option.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Cute Bros 2 Player', 4651, 'In this adventure, two siblings need to find all the necessary items. Each sibling must locate their own special key. After finding the keys, they must reach the chests. Before finding the keys and chests, they need to collect all the green coins along the way. The siblings must survive the challenges of the forest and reach the finish line safely. At the end, a floating portal awaits them.', 'Players use WASD AND Arrow key keys to move Mobile gameplay mobile touch control is available Open all the chests', 'English'),
('Mr. Bean Hidden Objects', 4652, 'Today in this game your task is to help the funny Mr. Bean to find the hidden objects. After entering one of the levels you have to find all the hidden objects. The names of the items you need to find will appear on the left side. You need to concentrate well and find all the objects. You have to watch the time, because if it runs out it will be game over. Try to get the maximum points and three stars in every level.', 'Click with your mouse or tap on the screen to find the objects', 'English'),
('Noob vs Pro HorseCraft', 4653, 'In this adventure, a noob and their closest friend, the Pro, are trying to reach and open a chest in a dangerous forest. The forest is so perilous that it could lead to their deaths, which they must avoid. Only the noob can assemble the key to the chest, so the noob needs to find all the pieces of the key. Meanwhile, with their powerful sword, the Pro can defeat all the monsters in the forest, ensuring a safer journey to the chest.', 'Use the WASD keys to move Press the P key to attack with the sword and throw the sword Mobile controls are available for playing on mobile Double jump is active in the game You can jump twice', 'English'),
('Meteorite Miner', 4654, 'Explore space by piloting a ship, collecting minerals, and avoiding traps. Rise from an office worker to a space miner, buy new ships, and upgrade your drill to become the best! Youll encounter numerous exciting levels and challenges on your way to the goal.', 'Right joystick Changes the ships direction Bottom-left joystick Accelerates the ship Top-left joystick Activates the force field to move the atomic battery', 'English'),
('Ice Hockey', 4655, 'Experience the thrill of the rink in Ice Hockey, an exciting arcade-style sports game! Glide across the ice, score goals, and defend your net in fast-paced hockey action. With dynamic gameplay and icy visuals, players can engage in quick single or multiplayer matches on a frozen hockey rink. Whether youre aiming for the perfect shot or blocking incoming pucks, this game is all about strategy, precision, and speed. Are you ready to lead your team to victory? Key Features: Single-player and multiplayer modes Fast-paced ice hockey action Cool icy aesthetics and animations Easy-to-learn controls for intense gameplay.', 'Player 1 Movement Use W to move up and S to move down Player 2 Movement Use the Up Arrow to move up and the Down Arrow to move down', 'English'),
('Sweet Princess Makeup Party', 4656, 'This is a make-up and dress-up game for girls. If you like princess styling, this game is for you.You need first to help our little princess get a facial, wash her hair, and design a fashionable look. Then you can access her wardrobe and help her match a stylish outfit.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Baby Panda Emotion World', 4657, 'This is an educational game for children. The game simulates real-life scenarios and helps children develop a friendly attitude toward others and master social etiquette. When friends come to visit your home, how do you entertain them?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Truck Stack Colors', 4658, 'Get ready for an exciting challenge. Truck Stack Colors takes you into a wonderful world of parkour and truck stacking. In attractive levels, advance by stacking platforms that are the same color as the truck. To master the balancing and stacking skills to build amazing truck towers and climb even higher.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Truck Simulator Construction', 4659, 'Truck Simulator Construction is a realistic simulation game where players take control of various heavy-duty trucks and machinery to complete challenging construction tasks. From transporting materials to operating cranes and excavators, players must manage time and resources to build structures, roads, and more. With immersive environments and detailed vehicles, experience the life of a construction site worker!', 'WASD - drive', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Mage Adventure: Mighty Raid', 4660, 'Mage Adventure: Mighty Raid is an action-packed blend of strategic combat and fast-paced survival. Stand your ground as waves of enemies rush toward you in a dynamic battlefield. Collect boosters to power up, unleash devastating attacks, and defeat epic bosses in thrilling, endless rooms. With each victory, your hero grows stronger, unlocking powerful abilities and equipment. Can you survive the onslaught and conquer the mighty raid? Test your skills in this addictive mix of strategy and action!', 'Tap on the screen to set per direction for projectiles', 'English'),
('Highschool Mean Girls 3', 4661, 'Play the Highschool Mean Girls 3 game and get ready to join 6 unique characters in the wild world of fashion drama in this brand-new dress-up game for girls. Test your fashion guru skills and transform high school wallflowers into show-stopping style icons. Rack up those style credits with a fabulous curated wardrobe and accessories. This dress-up game is where high school drama meets fashion week, straight from your screen. Happy playing!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('KaI Archer', 4662, 'Explore the wonder world of nature and find the hidden key. Are you ready to go through the mysterious adventure? Let&amp;rsquo;s deep dive into an amazing adventure. Avoid traps and spikes. Collect the key to open the door and visit the next level. Be Careful! Falling into the traps will over the game. If you like genres such as adventure, action, rpg, platform, quests or just want to have a good time then this game is for you. Features of this game: High Quality graphics Game size is minimal Super simple controls Interesting quests', 'How to play Android Use On-Screen touch buttons to control the player PC Move Left - Press ldquo A rdquo Move Right - Press ldquo D rdquo Jump - Press ldquo W rdquo', 'English'),
('Bee vs flying saucers', 4663, 'It&amp;rsquo;s harvest season, and the bees need your help! In this thrilling arcade game, guide a brave bee through dangerous fields filled with obstacles and invading flying saucers. Collect as many flowers as you can and defend your hive! Game Features: - Intuitive Controls: Tap the screen to make the bee rise and shoot. - Exciting Challenges: Avoid thorny plants and destroy flying saucers. - Vibrant Graphics: Enjoy a colorful and animated world. - Endless Levels: Every game is a new adventure! Are you ready for the challenge? Download Bee vs Flying Saucers now and show off your skills. Help the bees save', 'Mouse click touch or space key', 'English'),
('Sandbox Island War', 4664, 'Get ready for a wonderful pixel battle in Pixel Island War! This strategy game brings you to a wonderful pixel world. Here your task is to conquer islands and expand your empire. Build bases, gather resources and prepare for fierce battles on different islands. For example, choose an island to place humans on. Humans will build towns and multiply. Choose sheep to produce wool and meat.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Starlight Quest', 4665, 'Starlight Quest is a visually enchanting space adventure where players navigate a glowing star through a starry night sky. The goal is to collect as many bright golden stars as possible while avoiding dark void stars and hazardous asteroids. Each level becomes more challenging as the sky fills with obstacles, testing the players reflexes and skill. The peaceful cosmic setting, with twinkling stars and a glowing crescent moon, creates an immersive experience that will keep you captivated as you aim for a high score in the vast universe.', 'Movement Players can swipe or tilt their device to move the glowing star up down left or right guiding it through the starry sky Goal Collect golden stars to earn points and avoid the dark void stars and asteroids to stay alive Restart Reload Tap', 'English'),
('Pumpkin Jack', 4666, 'In this game, you take control of Jack the Pumpkin, navigating a unique world that revolves around your character. As you move, Jack clings to the ground, guided by gravity. Use this to your advantage to transition smoothly from one platform to another. Your goal is to explore the landscape, collect all the hidden pearls, and complete every challenging level. With each new area, you&amp;rsquo;ll encounter fresh obstacles and surprises that will test your skills and strategy. Dive into this fun, adventure-filled game, and enjoy exploring every corner of this exciting world!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('GoldPuzzle', 4667, 'A sparkling gold puzzle game that collects gold by eliminating gold nugets. Drag gold to fill the line or column, eliminate and collect gold, you can collect gold, pin gold and purple gold, their prices are different, when can not continue can consume gold replacement gold nugget, can also watch the advertisement to get a new gold nugget, each elimination reaches a certain amount will have an additional reward', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Superhero Race 2', 4668, 'Superhero Race is an exciting parkour adventure where you transform into various superheroes.Villains are taking over the world! We need heroes to clean up the mess they created. Every hero has unique abilities.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Meme Challenge Dank Memes', 4669, 'Meme Challenge: Dank Memes is a fun and casual card game! Designed for those who like to be funny and humorous! You will beat your opponents with the funniest memes. And show your sense of humor and creativity.Each game you will choose the funny emoji card that best fits the situation from your group of cards.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
