('Color Mix', 4670, 'Welcome to Color Mix brain game! This coloring puzzle game will teach you what color you get when you mix two colors. Explore tons of amazing and challenging levels and try to complete them all. Enjoy!', 'Tap or mouse click to play', 'English'),
('Monster Truck Speed Stunt', 4671, 'Monster Truck Speed Stunt is an adrenaline-pumping event where massive trucks race through obstacle-filled tracks, showcasing extreme power and agility. These colossal vehicles soar over ramps, crush cars, and perform gravity-defying jumps. Drivers push their trucks to the limit, reaching top speeds while maintaining control. The stunts combine speed, precision, and brute force, thrilling audiences with daring tricks like wheelies, donuts, and high-speed crashes across challenging terrains.', 'WASD to drive and use button in game to jump', 'English'),
('Sharpshot Trials', 4672, 'Step into the world of precision and power in Sharpshot Trials! This arrow-throwing challenge puts your aim to the test across a variety of dynamic scenarios. From moving targets to tricky angles, each level demands focus, timing, and a steady hand. With every accurate shot, you climb higher in skill and score &amp;mdash; but miss your mark, and the trial gets tougher. Are you ready to prove your mastery as the ultimate sharpshooter?', 'Aim and shoot', 'English'),
('Bubble Popper', 4673, 'Pop colorful bubbles to clear each level! Click or tap bubbles to make them disappear - smaller bubbles give more points, so aim carefully. Clear all bubbles to advance to the next level, where youll face more bubbles moving faster. Challenge yourself to achieve the highest score in this addictive arcade game perfect for quick gaming sessions!', 'Click or tap the bubbles to pop them', 'English'),
('flappy climate', 4674, 'The game is Flappy weather, you can play the flappy bird liked games , so this game also so fun and especially this game as one new thing is if you can hit the obstacles you can continue the game up to 3 lives . when the score is 10 greater the climate effects also changed. so much fun and addictive game . Thanking you.', 'In windows use mouse left click and android devices touch controls', 'English'),
('Goal.io', 4675, 'Goal.io &amp;ndash; Score Big in This Free Football IO Game Online Looking for a fast-paced soccer game you can play right in your browser? Meet Goal.io &amp;mdash; the ultimate free football io game online where reflexes, timing, and sharp shooting decide who rules the leaderboard. No downloads. No sign-ups. Just you, the ball, and 3 minutes to score big.', 'WADS to move', 'English'),
('Brainrot A Difference Challenge', 4676, 'Put your observation skills to the test in Brainrot &amp;ndash; A Difference Challenge, the ultimate photo puzzle game! Spot subtle differences between two eerily similar Italian brainrot images across a series of mind-bending levels. Each pair of pictures will challenge your focus, attention to detail, and visual memory. Can you find them all before time runs out?', 'Use a mouse or touch pad to play this game', 'English'),
('Tung Tung Sahur in Geometry Dash', 4677, 'Join Tung Tung Sahur, the wooden drum-carrying dawn caller, as he bounces and flips through a neon cityscape just before sunrise! Dodge spikes, leap over traps, and time your jumps to the beat of his signature &amp;ldquo;tung-tung!&amp;rdquo; calls. In this Geometry Dash&amp;ndash;inspired challenge, the streets are alive with glowing gates, speed pads, and tricky gravity flips. Can you drum your way to the end without missing a beat?', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Screw Nuts Bolts: Wood Solve', 4678, 'Embark on a Brain-Twisting Journey with Nuts and Bolts Woody Puzzle, an exceptional wood puzzle game about nuts and bolts to test your IQ brain power. For nuts and bolts lovers who likes challenge and innovative gameplay, the right game for you - the ultimate puzzle game - is here.', 'Start by tapping to remove nuts and bolts making the wood plates pinned to the board to cascade The complexity of the nuts and bolts within this puzzle game will test your wit Navigate the nuts and bolts correctly ensuring all wood plates fall This', 'English'),
('Burger Rush Restaurant', 4679, 'Welcome to your burger paradise! Dive into the sizzling world of restaurant management where every burger tells a story. Craft mouthwatering creations from a diverse range of ingredients, meeting each customers unique taste buds. Serve fast, combine cleverly, and watch your tiny burger joint grow into the town&amp;rsquo;s favorite spot for delicious burgers. Your burger mastery starts now!', 'Touch Click the ingredients to make a burger and click the customer to serve it', 'English');
