('RGB Shooter', 4680, 'RGB Shooter is a fast-paced 2D action shooting game where color-matching meets arcade chaos! Switch between red, green, and blue bullets to destroy enemies of the same color. Use your reflexes to survive endless waves of colorful attackers. As you level up, the game becomes faster and more challenging. Activate your Ulti ability to fire random-colored bullets and turn the tide of battle when things get intense. Simple controls, vibrant visuals, and addictive gameplay make RGB Shooter a perfect experience for action and arcade fans!', 'A ndash Krmz mermiyle ate et S ndash Yeil mermiyle ate et D ndash Mavi mermiyle ate et W ndash Ultiyi Aktif Et rastgele renkli mermi atar Bu kontroller ekrandaki butonlara tklanarak da kullanlabilir', 'English'),
('Buddy Kick Archer', 4681, 'Buddy Kick Archer is a fun and fast-paced archery challenge where you aim, shoot, and defeat quirky enemies with precision shots. Test your bow skills, unlock powerful arrows, and take down targets in creative ways. Perfect for players who love skill-based action mixed with humor and endless challenges in each level.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('BTC clicker', 4682, 'Click the Bitcoin and do upgrades like autoclicker and Bitcoin per click, and you have achievements like getting 100 Bitcoin , so what are you waiting for? Start clicking! :D', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('GhosTrick The Sacred War', 4683, 'Game Overview Players can choose to play against the computer (P1 vs CPU) or against another player (P1 vs P2). The game revolves around capturing each others pieces. However, not all pieces can be captured&amp;mdash;some must not be taken. Additionally, certain pieces have special roles or ranks. The victory conditions are as follows: Force your opponent to capture all of your forbidden-to-capture pieces. Capture a set number of the opponent&amp;rsquo;s valid targets. Successfully guide a specific number of your own pieces to the designated escape points.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Bricks of Wrath', 4684, 'Unleash chaos in Bricks of Wrath &amp;mdash; a break-brick game with a fierce twist! Fire powerful shots to destroy the advancing wall of bricks, but stay alert &amp;mdash; these aren&amp;rsquo;t ordinary bricks. Once attacked, they strike back! Dodge incoming fire, time your shots, and survive the relentless onslaught. With every level, the challenge intensifies. It&amp;rsquo;s not just about breaking bricks &amp;mdash; it&amp;rsquo;s about outlasting their wrath. How long can you hold your ground?', 'Shoot and avoid getting shot by the enemy', 'English'),
('Mission Kill Italian Brainrot', 4685, 'Hello warrior, help Tung Tung and defeat all the incoming enemies. There are enemies everywhere so you must be very careful. Destroy the enemies and find all the chests. You need to find and open all the chests. Open all the chests and collect the money inside. You must collect all the money dropped by the enemies. Gather the money and complete the level. In each level you will face stronger enemies, so you need to be even more careful. Save up money and buy different weapons.', 'Use the WASD keys to move Use the mouse to shoot Eliminate all enemies and collect all the gold to move to the next level 4 different game modes with 4 different difficulty levels rdquo', 'English'),
('Choco Draw', 4686, 'Welcome to Choco Draw, the sweetest twist on classic card games! In this candy-themed challenge, each card is marked with delicious treats &amp;mdash; from gummies and lollipops to chocolate bars and bonbons. Match, draw, and strategize your way through sugary showdowns where luck meets logic. Whether youre collecting sets or bluffing your way to victory, every draw is a bite-sized surprise. Ready to outsmart your opponents in this candy-coated card game?', 'Poker Game Enjoy', 'English'),
('Gun Match Screw', 4687, 'Gun Match Screw is a unique level-based puzzle game that combines screw puzzles with exciting gun-themed mechanics. In this game, each level presents you with a board shaped like different guns or gun parts, and your goal is to unlock all the boards by matching colored screws, which are represented as bullets. Gameplay: Each board contains a set of colored screws (bullets) that need to be matched to unlock the panels. The game features two modes where you fill 6-slot bullet magazines. By matching screws of the same color, youll fill the magazine and exchange it for a new empty one. You also have 5 extra bullet slots to store unmatched bu', 'Use left mouse button to play the game', 'English'),
('Minesweeper Infinite', 4688, '&amp;ldquo;Minesweeper Infinite&amp;rdquo; is a classic logic game with the addition of a new endless field mode! Now you have the opportunity to open cages and mine as much as you want. Overcome obstacles, compete with players from all over the world and take high positions on the leaderboard, showing everyone your unsurpassed strategy and ingenuity. Thanks to the simple and intuitive controls, everyone will be able to join this exciting process and test their strength in solving complex puzzles. Enjoy the pleasant design and stunning graphics and become a true professional in the world of &amp;ldquo;Minesweeper Infinite&amp;rdquo;!', '1 Select the mode Classic Endless 2 To open a cell click on it if there is a mine the game is over To find a mine use hints in the form of numbers of cells around for example if the number 1 is indicated in an open cell this means that one of t', 'English'),
('Dead Zone15165', 4689, 'Dead Zone is a lightweight 2D zombie shooter designed for instant browser play. Players control a lone survivor in a cartoon-style world, dodging and shooting waves of undead with simple one-button mechanics. Built for fast reflexes and short sessions, Dead Zone runs smoothly even on low-end devices .', 'Controls Move WASD or ZQSD Shoot Left Click Shift run Reload R Pause P Restart I Recover mouse control Tab if the mouse gets stuck', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Apple Worm 2', 4690, 'Play Apple Worm now. This is a classic puzzle game with simple operation. Brain-burning levels make you love it! Control a cute little worm whose goal is to eat the apple and upgrade. Upgrading allows you to unlock more cute skins. You can also earn rewards by completing challenges. Unlock Auto ATK, Summoning, etc.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Lafufu Typer', 4691, 'Your goal is to quickly match the correct letters of the colorful and chaotic Lafufus before they reach the barrier and break through your defenses, ending the game and your progress.', 'Use keyboard or touch to play', 'English'),
('Elvis Funny Face', 4692, 'Elvis Funny Face is super fun and free to play online game for kids. Make the funniest face of our Elvis and have fun!', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Wednesday Light Academia', 4693, 'Join the trend in Wednesday Light Academia - a fun, immersive makeover game for girls! Today youre becoming a super-talented stylist and your job is to transform Wednesday Addams from a dark e-girl look to a stunning girly-girl fashionista. Explore the fun realms of makeup, hairstyling, and fashion-forward wardrobe choices with this addictive game. Have fun!', 'Use your mouse to play the game on a desktop tap to play on mobile devices', 'English'),
('CloneUp: Stack Yourself', 4694, 'CloneUp &amp;ndash; Stack Yourself is a 2D pixel-art platformer where your greatest tool is&amp;hellip; yourself! Create clones, stack them, and use them as platforms to dodge spikes, reach new heights, and make your way to the exit door. In CloneUp &amp;ndash; Stack Yourself, you&amp;rsquo;ll use copies of the main character to reach platforms and avoid deadly obstacles. For some unknown reason, you have the power to create clones of yourself and even stack them to form makeshift platforms. Use them to cross dangerous gaps, escape spikes, and climb higher toward the goal. Your mission: reach the exit door on each level, using your reflexes, logic, and clever clone placement.', '- Move A D or larr rarr - Jump W uarr or Spacebar - Create Clone F Restart Level R Return to Menu P', 'English'),
('Creep Crushers', 4695, 'Step into the spooky showdown of Creep Crusher! Halloween horrors are closing in, and your only defense is your lightning-fast clicking skills. Tap repeatedly to smash ghouls, banish ghosts, and squash creepy creatures before they get too close. Every enemy you crush keeps you safe a little longer, but as the night deepens, the creeps come faster and in greater numbers. Can you survive the haunting onslaught and become the ultimate Halloween hero?', 'Click on the pumpkins', 'English'),
('FireEgg', 4696, 'Control the chicken to fire bullets, smashing obstacles from all directions. The more obstacles you smash, the more gold coins you will obtain. Gold coins can be used to upgrade the bullet firing frequency furnace, as well as the bullet damage and rotation frequency. Its very fun. Come and give it a try', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Help sprunky', 4697, 'Get ready for an exciting and challenging challenge! This puzzle game will test your wits and attentiveness as you help the characters complete levels with mazes, solve problems and collect important items. Simple controls, high difficulty: Easy to play: Tap and hold the characters head, then pull to move. When you release, the head automatically returns to its starting position, creating a simple but tricky control mechanism. Mazes and traps: Each level has a confusing maze with obstacles and traps through which you need to guide your character to collect the desired item.', 'ap and hold the characters head with your finger on your phone or mouse on your PC Avoid the traps and collect the necessary item to complete the level', 'English'),
('Italian Brainrot Survival Arena', 4698, 'Are you ready for the ultimate showdown between Trallero and Tung Tung Sahur? Yes, in a lava-filled cave &amp;mdash; let&amp;rsquo;s see who will win! The player who falls into the lava the most loses the game. You can push your friend. Push your friend and make them fall into the lava. Be very careful! Avoid falling into the lava at all costs. Remember, it&amp;rsquo;s not just the danger of falling down &amp;mdash; you also have to watch out for rocket missiles falling from the cave ceiling. If one of them hits you, you lose the game.', 'Use the WASD or Arrow keys to move Press S or the Down arrow key to push each other The player who falls into the lava the most or gets hit by a rocket loses the game Playable on both mobile and PC', 'English'),
('Monster Jeep Coloring', 4699, 'Monster Jeep Coloring is a playful online game made for kids who love creativity. Pick your favorite monster jeep image and bring it to life with your own colors. Once your masterpiece is ready, share it proudly with friends. Let your imagination run wild and enjoy the fun of coloring!', 'Mouse to play', 'English');
