('Snowcraft   2 Player', 4861, 'In the world of Snowcraft, it&amp;rsquo;s snowing and the temperature is dropping rapidly. Steve and Alex need to be very careful. They must reach the portal before they freeze. Steve can use his sword to defeat the snowman monsters. Defeat all the snowman monsters and reach the end of the level. The snowman monsters are very smart and are constantly wandering through the snowy forest. Use your sword to kill them. Collect all the coins. Gather all the coins and reach the portal.', 'Use the WASD keys to move Press the P key to attack with the sword and throw the sword Mobile controls are available for playing on mobile Double jump is active in the game You can jump twice', 'English'),
('Water Slide Adventure', 4862, 'Dive into the ultimate water slide adventure with Extreme Water Slide Adventure! Experience the thrill of speeding down giant slides in this offline swimming pool game. As a super slider, youll navigate crazy twists, turns, and daring stunts that will keep you on the edge of your seat. Packed with excitement and fun, this game offers endless enjoyment for all water slide enthusiasts. Are you ready for the ride of your life?', 'WASD - CONTROL the player', 'English'),
('MultiplyBalls', 4863, 'Dive into the captivating world of MultiplyBalls, where every touch sets off a mesmerizing chain reaction! Navigate through the challenge as you control a ball, multiplying its presence with every tap.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Super Hero Sponge', 4864, 'Join the action-packed adventure with Super Hero Sponge! Embark on an epic journey as the brave sponge hero, battling against formidable enemies and monstrous Big Bosses. Team up with friends, overcome challenging obstacles, and save the day with your heroic skills. With thrilling gameplay and exciting challenges, this adventure is perfect for fans of action and fun. Are you ready to become the ultimate Super Hero Sponge? Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.kizi10.org/''&gt;https://www.kizi10.org/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Controlls WASD Walk X Attack F Fire SPACE Jump', 'English'),
('Car Out', 4865, 'Get ready for a high-octane adventure with Car Out, the ultimate driving challenge that will test your skills and reflexes! In this action-packed HTML game, you&amp;rsquo;re tasked with navigating a series of increasingly complex obstacle courses while avoiding hazards and collecting power-ups. Can you make it to the finish line and earn the title of top driver? By Gamezad.com', 'solve All levels', 'English'),
('RumDreams', 4866, 'In RumDreams, you control a little green blob of goo that navigates a dangerous 2D platform world. The environment is full of sharp spikes, moving spiky walls and strange floating eyes that fire projectiles. Your goal is to collect three glowing energy balls scattered throughout each stage while dodging these dangers. Gameplay involves precise jumping, timing and strategic moves to avoid instant death from the dangerous obstacles. Each stage increases in difficulty, challenging your reflexes and puzzle-solving skills as you help the goo escape this strange and hostile world.', 'W and jump D and walk to the right A and walk left U deactivates and activates the sound X restarts the phase', 'English'),
('Turbo Race', 4867, 'Get ready to burn rubber in Turbo race, the ultimate racing experience of the fastest and most powerful cars in the world. Whether youre a casual gamer or a hardcore racing enthusiast. Race through a variety of stunning locations, each with its own unique challenges. The game features realistic physics, breathtaking graphics, and immersive sound effects. Compete with AI cars and rise to the top of the racing world. Turbo Race promises endless hours of high-octane entertainment. Download Turbo Race today on Desktops &amp;amp; Mobile.', 'To control the car on a desktop simply move your mouse cursor to steer the vehicle and keep it on the track The car responds to the direction of your cursor so precise movements will help you navigate tight turns and avoid obstacles On a mobile device', 'English'),
('Power Link', 4868, 'Power Link is an electrifying puzzle game that challenges players to connect circuits and light up bulbs using limited moves. Set in a futuristic neon world, players must strategically connect energy sources to light up all the bulbs on each level. With increasingly complex puzzles, Power Link offers hours of brain-teasing fun, testing your logic and problem-solving skills.', 'Objective Connect all the plugs to the extensions using the available moves to light them up Controls Tap and drag to connect the plugs and extensions Ensure all extensions are connected before running out of moves', 'English'),
('starpoly', 4869, 'Pc trading board game which can be played against AI and among family and friends.contains unique features such as lottery and appreciation of properties draws.accept or decline loan and the starbridge.Use site management to settle amount,upgrade,downgrade and sell properties which can be done also by clicking on the corresponding sites/slots.Relax n enjoy A', 'Mouse click to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
