('Stunt Maps', 4904, 'Stunt Maps Get ready to defy gravity and push your skills to the limit with Stunt Maps, the ultimate stunt driving experience! Jump into a world of high-octane action, where you&amp;rsquo;ll soar through the skies, navigate impossible loops, and perform jaw-dropping stunts on mind-bending maps. Whether youre racing against time or just showing off your best tricks.', 'Driving W A S D Keys Or Arrow Keys Respawning Hold R Until Respawn Bar Fills To End', 'English'),
('Shape Transform Blob Racing', 4905, 'Shape Transform: Blob Racing is a casual running game. In this game, you will control a little Blob, running, shape-shifting, and go through various challenges!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
