('Hole Io 2', 4955, 'Hole.io is a super addictive free arcade game. If you were to ask what game is the most popular these days? Then its the black hole devouring game that has exploded in popularity worldwide.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Fall Fu Panda', 4956, 'Fall Fu Panda is a captivating game where the world revolves, and your character must fall into place. In this game, you&amp;rsquo;ll experience dynamic rotating physics, allowing you to zoom out and view the entire world, track your players position, and follow their every move as they navigate the environment. The goal is to land on objects to score points or defeat enemies. Picture your hero trying to escape from a dungeon or cave, overcoming obstacles in a constantly shifting world. To play, simply tap the left or right side of the screen to rotate the world, making your character fall onto the next block. If they miss and fall off, it&amp;rsquo;s game ove', 'Touch Left Key Left Left Rotate Left Touch Right Key Right Rotate Right', 'English'),
