('Granny Chapter 3 High School', 4958, 'Chapter 3: High School Escape from Granny is a fun third-person horror game where you must hide from Granny and the specters of Slendrina. Discover the keys to the abandoned schools classrooms, stock up on ammo, and try to stay alive for as long as possible. Find the revolver loaded with ammo and all the keys to the classrooms of the vacant school while Granny and Slendrina chase you. As you go inside the classroom, youll see a single desk that reads Granny and the keys to the locked door. Finally, Slendrina or Granny makes the player', 'The main objective of the game is to try to survive as long as you can by collecting items to hide and escape from Granny Controls WASD to move Right click to shoot F Interact Esc Menu', 'English'),
